				</span><span class='av-structured-data'  itemprop="author" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/Person" ><span itemprop='name'>Eric Lendrum</span></span><span class='av-structured-data'  itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2020-06-04T05:26:01-07:00" >2020-06-04 05:26:01</span><span class='av-structured-data'  itemprop="dateModified" itemtype="https://schema.org/dateModified" >2020-06-04 06:01:38</span><span class='av-structured-data'  itemprop="mainEntityOfPage" itemtype="https://schema.org/mainEntityOfPage" ><span itemprop='name'>Three More NYPD Officers Attacked by Rioters</span></span></span></article><article class='post-entry post-entry-type-standard post-entry-61080 post-loop-4 post-parity-even multi-big with-slider post-61080 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news homepage_placement-news'  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/BlogPosting" itemprop="blogPost" ><div class="big-preview multi-big"><a href="https://amgreatness.com/2020/06/04/rioter-in-texas-repeatedly-threatened-violence-against-president-trump-and-his-supporters/"  title="(Photo by AAron Ontiveroz/MediaNews Group/The Denver Post via Getty Images)" ><img width="635" height="423" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20635%20423'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-entry_without_sidebar size-entry_without_sidebar wp-post-image" alt="" data-lazy-srcset="https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat.jpg 5505w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-300x200.jpg 300w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-768x512.jpg 768w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-200x133.jpg 200w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-400x267.jpg 400w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-600x400.jpg 600w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-800x533.jpg 800w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-1200x800.jpg 1200w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-675x450.jpg 675w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 635px) 100vw, 635px" data-lazy-src="https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat.jpg" /><noscript><img width="635" height="423" src="https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat.jpg" class="attachment-entry_without_sidebar size-entry_without_sidebar wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat.jpg 5505w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-300x200.jpg 300w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-768x512.jpg 768w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-200x133.jpg 200w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-400x267.jpg 400w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-600x400.jpg 600w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-800x533.jpg 800w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-1200x800.jpg 1200w, https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/08/MAGAHat-675x450.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 635px) 100vw, 635px" /></noscript></a></div><div class='blog-meta'></div><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix standard-content'><header class="entry-content-header">
