<p>Oh, ok. <a href="https://www.foxnews.com/us/texas-man-with-assault-rifle-at-george-floyd-protest-allegedly-plotted-to-off-racists-and-maga-people">Texas man with &#8216;assault rifle&#8217; at George Floyd protest allegedly plotted &#8216;to off racists and MAGA people&#8217;</a></p>
