				</span><span class='av-structured-data'  itemprop="author" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/Person" ><span itemprop='name'>Liz Sheld</span></span><span class='av-structured-data'  itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2020-06-04T03:20:14-07:00" >2020-06-04 03:20:14</span><span class='av-structured-data'  itemprop="dateModified" itemtype="https://schema.org/dateModified" >2020-06-04 03:20:14</span><span class='av-structured-data'  itemprop="mainEntityOfPage" itemtype="https://schema.org/mainEntityOfPage" ><span itemprop='name'>Morning Greatness: Charges Escalated, More Cops Arrested for Floyd Death</span></span></span></article><article class='post-entry post-entry-type-standard post-entry-61073 post-loop-7 post-parity-odd multi-big with-slider post-61073 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news homepage_placement-news'  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/BlogPosting" itemprop="blogPost" ><div class="big-preview multi-big"><a href="https://amgreatness.com/2020/06/04/celebrities-sign-defund-the-police-letter/"  title="Getty Images" ><img width="533" height="301" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20533%20301'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-entry_without_sidebar size-entry_without_sidebar wp-post-image" alt="" data-lazy-src="https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/04/HollywoodSignX-e1555415132782.jpg" /><noscript><img width="533" height="301" src="https://overland.amgreatness.com/app/uploads/2019/04/HollywoodSignX-e1555415132782.jpg" class="attachment-entry_without_sidebar size-entry_without_sidebar wp-post-image" alt="" /></noscript></a></div><div class='blog-meta'></div><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix standard-content'><header class="entry-content-header">
