<p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p>
<p>Shockingly, the mayor&#8217;s own daughter Chiara de Blasio was <a href="https://nypost.com/2020/05/31/mayor-de-blasios-daughter-chiara-arrested-at-manhattan-protest/">arrested over the weekend</a> for allegedly blocking traffic and refusing to move. Her mugshot is below.</p>
<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true">
