<p>&mdash; Andy Ngô (@MrAndyNgo) <a href="https://twitter.com/MrAndyNgo/status/1267860922929840130?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">June 2, 2020</a></p></blockquote>
<p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p>
<p>Tuesday night, the anarchy continued but was more subdued because of the earlier 8:00 curfew.</p>
