<p>Oddly enough, one group of looters showed up at a store in the SoHo neighborhood in<a href="https://disrn.com/news/nyc-looters-pull-up-in-350000-rolls-royce-to-ransack-store"> a $350,000 Rolls-Royce.</a></p>
